videos.headline: Northwestern strikes first after 36-yard completion
videos.description: JJ Jefferson takes a bubble screen to the 1-yard line, and then Clayton Thorson finishes the drive on a quarterback sneak to make it 7-0 Wildcats.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Northwestern strikes first after 36-yard completion) 2018/09/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Northwestern adds to lead with 3-yard TD run
videos.description: John Moten IV gets through a lane and crosses the goal line to increase the Wildcats' lead over Michigan to 17-0.
